## Description {#details}

Represents a search that terminated after finding a clobber.

This clobber may or may not be present in the path of defs from LastNode..SearchStart, since it may have been retrieved from cache.

Definition at line 607 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/analysis/memoryssa-cpp">MemorySSA.cpp</a>.
